snippet.title: Beyond the Phone Screen (Game Trailer)
snippet.description:
Play now at https://davidrodmad.itch.io/beyond-the-phone-screen

Retro horror game about a Pokemon Go-style app, made by David Rodríguez Madriñán, David García Láuzara and Perfecto Carballo Oliveira

80 bpm doom-industrial groove by Akirawakira
Abstract industrial music by szegvari
